-- Yemen Security Forces Surround Parcel Suspect's Home, President Saleh Says
-- B y   M o h a m m e d   H a t e m   H a s a n   A l i
-- 2010-10-30T17:42:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-30/yemen-security-forces-surround-parcel-suspect-s-home-president-saleh-says.html
Yemeni security forces have
surrounded the house of a woman who sent two parcel bombs to the
U.S., President Ali Abdullah Saleh said at a press conference in
Sana’a today.  Saleh said he expects the woman to be arrested at her home
in the nation’s capital within the next several hours.  To contact the reporter on this story:
